to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"the Leonardo da Vinci painting\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"his apostles\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics organisers have said there was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\" and the intent was to \\\"celebrate community tolerance\\\".\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the intent\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch's lawyer, Audrey Msellati, said the complaint was filed with the Paris prosecutor's office, which must then decide whether it warrants a formal police investigation.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"score\": 0.768291763107565, \"rank\": 0.30158885977086763, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.078626157865024e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch's lawyer\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"a formal police investigation\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The DJ said she was \\\"honoured to take part in the Paris 2024 opening ceremony\\\" but the messages she has received \\\"are increasingly extreme\\\".\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9864662518081188, \"rank\": 0.013719423400139154, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3606372652704184e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the messages\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Msellati said in a statement, posted to Butch's Instagram: \\\"Since the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, artist, DJ, and activist Barbara Butch has been the target of an extremely violent campaign of cyber-harassment and defamation.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6028537083874393e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Msellati\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"artist\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"DJ\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"an extremely violent campaign\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber-harassment\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"defamation\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has been threatened with death, torture, and rape, and has also been the target of numerous antisemitic, homophobic, sexist, and grossophobic insults.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous antisemitic, homophobic, sexist, and grossophobic insults\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Barbara Butch condemns this vile hatred directed at her, what she represents, and what she stands for.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this vile hatred\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Indeed, her commitments and personal values of benevolence, inclusivity and love for others have always been at the heart of her artistic project: promoting festivities for all, regardless of age, sexual orientation, origin, religion or gender.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her commitments\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"personal values\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"benevolence\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"her artistic project\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"festivities\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is today filing several complaints against these acts, whether committed by French nationals or foreigners, and intends to prosecute anyone who tries to intimidate her in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9883526698484991, \"rank\": 0.011751739254016482, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several complaints\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"these acts\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch said on her Instagram page: \\\"I was extremely honoured to take part in the Paris 2024 opening ceremony as a top artist, and to share my vision of the party.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2001, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6028537083874393e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3606372652704184e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"a top artist\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"my vision\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the party\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My heart is still full of joy and I thank you for all the love and strength you have given me since then.\\\"\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My heart\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"all the love\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about the complaint, she added: \\\"Although at first I decided not to speak out to let the haters cool down, the messages I receive are increasingly extreme.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"the haters\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the messages\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All because I have had the honour of representing my country's diversity through art and music, alongside other artists and performers I admire.\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the honour\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"my country's diversity\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"other artists\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whatever some may say, I exist.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whatever\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never been ashamed of who I am, and I take responsibility for everything - including my artistic choices.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"my artistic choices\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All my life, I have refused to be a victim: I will not shut up.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a victim\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not afraid of those who hide behind a screen, or a pseudonym, to spew their hatred and frustrations.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a screen\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"a pseudonym\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"their hatred\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"frustrations\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will fight them without ever trembling.\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am committed, and I am proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023 the DJ was honoured as a Pride Icon at the Attitude Pride Awards and told the publication she was forced to close her restaurant in the south of France due to homophobia.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2976, 